description: The Flagship ETH Morpho vault curated by B.Protocol and Block Analitica is intended to optimize risk-adjusted interest earned from blue-chip LST and stablecoin collateral markets. The Flagship ETH vault also serves as a pre-deposit vault for Relend Network. Users who supply ETH will collect RELEND units and have the option to access Relend Network once live.
The Re7 cbBTC vault curated by Re7 Labs aims to provide an above-market cbBTC yield by enabling leveraged-yield strategies and supporting high-yield cbBTC markets.
The Re7 Resolv USR vault supplies USR to various collateral markets with a focus on the Resolv Protocol ecosystem.

The MEV Capital M^0 vault curated by MEV Capital is dedicated to providing capital to M^0 protocol markets. It offers borrowers access to attractive rates through M^0 incentives and provides suppliers with a competitive APR.

The cbBTC Core Vault will whitelist a range of liquid collateral markets and continuously optimize risk-adjusted yield across those markets. This vault targets a higher risk level than Gauntlet's Prime Vaults.

The SwissBorg tBTC vault optimizes risk-adjusted returns in BTC derivative collateral markets through dynamic asset allocation and adherence to Gauntlet's risk management protocols. Access the vault via the SwissBorg App.

The Index Coop High Yield ETH Index (hyETH) is a Gauntlet curated vault that optimizes risk-adjusted yield for ETH holders by allocating deposits across high-yield lending opportunities. Gauntlet uses its expertise to actively manage allocations, targeting diverse markets with stable yields above the Lido staking rate. Deposit into the vault via the Index Coop App Site for optimal performance.

The Gauntlet WETH Ecosystem Vault is designed to optimize risk-adjusted yields by leveraging liquid staking recursive yield markets while enabling a broader range of integrations through the v1.1 upgrade. For further insights into Gauntlet's curated strategies, visit the forum.
